{"tid":430420,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林嘉欣似自己打咗場","createTime":"2017-10-09T18:00:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-09T22:42:33.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e2cf7617ab63384b5ffdafd5f6a0131e3c6b9d5c","tid":430420,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T18:00:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20171009/20176537\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20171009%2F20176537&d=4LEb4YyAUYZV8NcSq2Ubhm6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=ba8418f9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fentertainment%2Fart%2F20171009%2F20176537&h=86d5ffcb\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/entertainment/art/20171009/20176537</a><br />\n<br />\n林嘉欣似自己打咗場<br />\n<br />\n9,476<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/apple-photos/apple/20171009/large/09ec1p6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20171009%2Flarge%2F09ec1p6.jpg&h=4bfa0cb7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■林嘉欣（中）揚言首次現場睇拳賽後，感覺如自己落場打一樣。互聯網圖片<br />\n<br />\n林嘉欣從未曾在現場睇過拳賽，前晚她卻為曹星如獻出第一次。對於有人質疑賽果造馬，她說：「我唔清楚賽制，所以冇嘢可以回應。」<br />\n<br />\n不過對於前晚拳賽，林嘉欣直指十分精采，她說：「之前做慈善都見過曹星如，我覺得佢台下台上係兩個人，台下佢有少少怕醜又好nice，台上好有風度。噚晚好似自己都打咗一場拳賽，睇見佢第二round眼睛都腫咗，好緊張，自己兩個拳頭揸到好實，睇完之後自己都好似打咗一場拳擊咁樣，都幾過癮。」  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n陳志雲撐實至名歸<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n林海峰：受傷仍堅持"},{"pid":"fe90210bd0cc95b52123dbea99b3d4d5fc623deb","tid":430420,"uid":20448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-09T22:42:33.000Z","msg":"好想同佢打返場 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}